@DATABASE "Kat-Trap"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - K - Kat-Trap"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - K
                   ====================================

                                 Kat-Trap
                                 ========



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Multi-POKE    " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(31039,45)"}          31039,45
@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPOKE(29362,128)"}          29362,x (x= 1-128)
@{"See End Screen" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPOKE(31040,0)"}          31040,0


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         The "Multi-POKE" gives you Infinite Lives
                         and Grenades.
                         (Pity it doesn't make the game any better!)


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
